{"tid":2310644,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"留守員工騎牛搵馬「勢爆第二波離職潮」","createTime":"2020-12-03T11:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T14:54:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3a07161f3c57f8b8b2ec3796a6eea1cded2d916a","tid":2310644,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:52:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201203/IZZGYILWWRBPVDT5F3PDJC5L4M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201203%2FIZZGYILWWRBPVDT5F3PDJC5L4M%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=7e395b90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201203%2FIZZGYILWWRBPVDT5F3PDJC5L4M%2F&h=d4b940b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201203/IZZGYILWWRBPVDT5F3PDJC5L4M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n留守員工騎牛搵馬「勢爆第二波離職潮」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7Wa-J8qxGxvEHl9Sn1xSgm1MXl4=/1570x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DROPMMMLNRAOLOATU6NMM23ZFI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7Wa-J8qxGxvEHl9Sn1xSgm1MXl4%3D%2F1570x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDROPMMMLNRAOLOATU6NMM23ZFI.jpg&h=3532d0da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■2017年《新聞刺針》有關動物傳心師的報道引起社會熱議。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】記者辭職困難，留下亦不容易。有留下的有線電視員工坦言，前日經歷戰友被裁，新聞部士氣愁雲慘霧，人心惶惶，相信現時絕大部份留低的員工在經濟不景下，各有包袱，只求「騎牛搵馬」，「已經唔係為守住啲乜嘢」。他相信，當辭職同事兩、三個月後離職，若屆時高層逼前線做有違良心或「舐共」的事，將會有第二波的離職潮。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：疑《刺針》滅組先兆「空降首日不聞不問」<br />\n<br />\n該員工透露，「換血一定會，。。。。。。。。。室，未解釋人事變動原因。<br />\n<br />\n任職有線港聞記。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：促唱好官派律師 蔡玉玲被捕不做頭條  許方輝入有線複製TVB<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n員工辭職 許方輝當做戲<br />\n<br />\n阿Z亦引述其他辭職同事指︰「佢會話『得㗎喇，你做咗呢個動作就得』，即係當你做戲，你點都要做啲嘢去回應我哋炒人，咁當你做咗啦，做場大龍鳳，但其實唔係，大家都係好想離開。」<br />\n<br />\n他又透露，有同事曾做過有關「12送中港人」家屬的訪問，許方輝卻指當中內容「煽情」，要求加入當事人所涉嫌的罪行、為何要潛逃等的資料，「我哋得三分鐘cast，佢就係想感受性嘅嘢少啲，你就會知佢係想點，佢都唔想啲古仔出」。"},{"pid":"d135790595691f7523f2d46535614c35121026d4","tid":2310644,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:53:45.000Z","msg":"攞埋年尾果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4321502d8674f43d19e5bfbf6845d904449bed36","tid":2310644,"uid":284575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d135790595691f7523f2d46535614c35121026d4","tid":2310644,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:53:45.000Z","msg":"攞埋年尾果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:59:19.000Z","msg":"有無得出都係問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲等俾人逼做有違良心或「舐共」的事，先有第二波的離職潮？是咪傻的？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b786b761e4afe6958eb027185b64141abb80351","tid":2310644,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4321502d8674f43d19e5bfbf6845d904449bed36","tid":2310644,"uid":284575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d135790595691f7523f2d46535614c35121026d4","tid":2310644,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:53:45.000Z","msg":"攞埋年尾果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:59:19.000Z","msg":"有無得出都係問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲等俾人逼做有違良心或「舐共」的事，先有第二波的離職潮？是咪傻的？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T14:41:03.000Z","msg":"其實剩低嗰8個好大機會只係幫離職同事做埋d手尾，出埋d報導就走<br />\n似係一齊傾出嚟嘅做法"},{"pid":"e6553b848a7162fd062f88ac277a81fc55c35244","tid":2310644,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T14:54:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dru